<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>LA Music</title>

    <style>
        #cafe{
            width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid #d6d6d6;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }
        span{
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        #cabecalho{

            /*display: flex;*/
            padding: 1em;
            align-items: center; /* Vertical center alignment */
            justify-content: center; /* Horizontal center alignment */
            
        }
        #titulo{
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;

            /*display: flex;*/
            align-items: center; /* Vertical center alignment */
            justify-content: center; /* Horizontal center alignment */
        }
        #corpo{
            /* height: 200px; */
            padding: 1em;
            /* display: flex; */
            align-items: center; /* Vertical center alignment */
            justify-content: center; /* Horizontal center alignment */
        }
        #footer{
            border-top:1px solid #d6d6d6 ;
            height: auto;
            padding: 2em;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        #logo{
            height: 65px;
        }
        #footer li{
            display: inline;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        #footer ul{
            text-align: center;
        }
        li{
            /* list-style: none; */
            margin: 1em;
        }
        ul{
            text-align: left;
        }
        div span{
            color: #767676;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 1em;
        }
        button{
            background-color: black;
            border-radius: 25px;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="cafe">
        <div id="cabecalho"> <img id="logo" src="http://www.lamusic.com.br/wp-content/themes/la_music/assets/img/matheus-logo-la.jpeg"></img></div>
        <div id="titulo"><h3>{{titulo}}</h3></div>
        <div id="corpo">
            <h3>Olá admin</h3>
            </br>    
            <p> O usuário: <b>{{perfil.nome}}</b>, da editora: <b>{{perfil.nome_empresa}}</b>, cpf: <b>{{perfil.cpf}}</b> quer contratar o LA Pro!</p> 
                
                </br>
                <p> Favor entrar em contato pelo email: <b>{{perfil.email}}</b> ou telefone: <b>{{perfil.telefone}}</b></p>
                </br>
                Nome do artista: <b>{{result.nome}}</b>
                </br>
                Cpf do artista: <b>{{result.cpf_cliente}}</b>
                </br>
                Lista de {{objeto}}:
                    <div>
                        {{#each lista}}
                            <ul>
                                <li>Titulo: {{this.titulo}}</li> 
                                <li>Ecad: {{this.codEcad}}</li> 
                                <li>Motivo: {{this.motivo}}</li> 
                            </ul>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </br>
                att, Sistema LA Music.
            </br>

        </div>
    </div> 
    
</body>
</html>